M|vercel-react-best-practices|Dashboard
M|vercel-react-best-practices|</a>
M|vercel-react-best-practices|</nav>
M|vercel-react-best-practices|)
M|vercel-react-best-practices|}
M|vercel-react-best-practices|```
M|vercel-react-best-practices|**When to use each:**
M|vercel-react-best-practices|| API | Use case |
M|vercel-react-best-practices||-----|----------|
M|vercel-react-best-practices|| `prefetchDNS` | Third-party domains you'll connect to later |
M|vercel-react-best-practices|| `preconnect` | APIs or CDNs you'll fetch from immediately |
M|vercel-react-best-practices|| `preload` | Critical resources needed for current page |
M|vercel-react-best-practices|| `preloadModule` | JS modules for likely next navigation |
