M|vercel-react-best-practices|const sorted = [...items].sort((a, b) => a.value - b.value)
M|vercel-react-best-practices|```
M|vercel-react-best-practices|`.toSorted()` is available in all modern browsers (Chrome 110+, Safari 16+, Firefox 115+, Node.js 20+). For older environments, use spread operator:
