M|vercel-react-best-practices|useEffect(() => {
M|vercel-react-best-practices|loadFromStorage()
M|vercel-react-best-practices|checkAuthToken()
M|vercel-react-best-practices|}, [])
M|vercel-react-best-practices|// ...
M|vercel-react-best-practices|}
M|vercel-react-best-practices|```
M|vercel-react-best-practices|**Correct: once per app load**
